_sText:
MAYBE THE BEST AIM MAP EVER? :D

ITS 100% ACCURATE TO THE ORIGINAL GAME, I MADE AN EXACT COPY PIXEL BY PIXEL, AND THE SPACE INVADERS ARE DESTROYABLE.

To install, copy the aim_spaceinvaders.bsp and the aim_spaceinvaders.bsp.bak   in the maps folder located in cstrike (counter-strike source\cstrike\maps)

This is the first map I have made and I hope you enjoy. :P

Revolver / Superfly / TMM
